        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about the International Symposium on Energy & Environment, need assistance with
          registration, or want to collaborate with us, feel free to reach out through the details below. </p>
      </div><!-- End Section Title -->

      <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">

